      <p>The <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01KFNKGZ0?tag=sciencesolved-20">Bosch Professional GSA 18V-LI C Reciprocating Saw</a> delivers 0 to 3,050 strokes per minute with a cutting depth of 200 mm in wood. At 329 ratings with 4.8 stars, it has strong reviews from tradespeople who value the Bosch Professional platform. The brushless motor extends runtime during prolonged pruning sessions, and the variable speed trigger with lock-on reduces fatigue during continuous cutting. The SDS tool-free blade change releases with one hand and accepts standard shank blades. For tree limbing, pair it with an 8-inch or 12-inch pruning blade. The saw weighs 6.4 pounds with battery, making it feasible for one-handed operation while balanced on a ladder cutting overhead limbs. <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01KFNKGZ0?tag=sciencesolved-20">Check current price on Amazon</a>.</p>

